6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Andi and Jasper Chat share a solid foundation of core features including . Where Andi pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Web Search and Citations, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Jasper Chat uniquely offers File Upload and Api Access and Memory and Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Andi holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Jasper Chat scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Andi offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Jasper Chat's starting price of $49/mo. Andi has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Jasper Chat does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
