a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Andi is best suited for simple search, visual answers, beginners, quick lookups, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Jasper Chat, meanwhile, shines for marketing teams, brand voice chat, content ideation, campaign planning, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2022, Andi describes itself as \"Visual AI search assistant that explains answers simply.\" Jasper Chat, established in 2023, positions itself as \"Marketing-focused AI chat integrated into Jasper platform.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Jasper Chat** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 5.0), more features (4 vs 2). However, this does not mean Andi is a poor choice — far from it. Andi excels in its own right, particularly for simple search and visual answers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value trained on marketing best practices, go with Jasper Chat. If clean visual interface for search results matters more to you, Andi is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
